Title: Pictures from the 1996 USJI Senior Nationals
Body: Date: Tue, 10 Dec 1996 17:52:48 GMT Server: NCSA/1.4.2 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Tue, 14 May 1996 18:09:39 GMT Content-length: 1123 Pictures from the 1996 USJI Senior Nationals 1996 USJI Senior National Judo Championships April 11-13 1996 - San Jose, California The floor of the San Jose State Event Center I recently had the opportunity to go to my first national tournament, and competed Friday afternoon in the Men's -95kg division.
